dct_title_s: South America, west coast, sheet III : from the Gulf of Peñas to the Guaytecas Islands
dct_description_sm: Relief shown by hachures. Depths shown by soundings. "1825"--Lower left margin. "From Kelly Harbour to Tres Montes is taken from the Beagle survey of 1828." Includes 5 coastal profiles. Historic Maps copy has label on verso: South America. Gulf of Penas to the Guaytecas Islands. Sheet 3. 1325.
dct_publisher_sm: [London] : Published according to Act of Parliament at the Hydrographic Office of the Admiralty ; Sold by R.B. Bate, agent for the Admiralty charts, Jany. 24th 1841.
